Personal life

Asher was first married to Danny Sue Nolan from 1951-1961, with whom he had two children. Asher then married Bewitched star Elizabeth Montgomery in 1963. They had three children and divorced in 1973 (soon after the series' cancellation). His third marriage was to Joyce Bulifant from 1976-1993. He adopted her son, actor, John Mallory Asher. In his last years, Asher resided in Palm Desert, California with his fourth wife, Meredith Asher.

